lead_paragraph: Inter Milan fired Dutchman Frank de Boer as coach on Tuesday after less than three months in charge during which the former European champions lost seven of their 14 competitive games.

headline.print_headline: De Boer Fired by Inter Milan After 14 Matches
headline.main: De Boer Fired by Inter Milan After 14 Matches
